---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Markdown Editor & Preview
description: Free online Markdown editor with live preview. Write and format Markdown with instant rendering. Supports GitHub Flavored Markdown.
keywords: markdown editor, markdown preview, markdown to html, GFM, github markdown, markdown converter, online markdown editor
permalink: /tools/markdown-preview/
toolId: markdown-preview
toolJs: markdown-preview.js
ogImage: markdown-preview.jpg
---
{# Get tool data from tools.json #}
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<!-- Schema.org BreadcrumbList -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Tools", "item": "{{ site.url }}/#tools"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "{{ toolData.name }}", "item": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}"}
  ]
}
</script>

<!-- Schema.org WebApplication -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "{{ toolData.fullName }}",
  "description": "{{ description }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}",
  "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any",
  "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript",
  "offers": {"@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD"},
  "author": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}"}
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
  .markdown-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); min-height: 500px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .markdown-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .markdown-panel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; }
  .markdown-panel-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .markdown-panel-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .markdown-editor { flex: 1; border: none; padding: var(--space-4); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.6; resize: none; background: var(--color-bg); }
  .markdown-editor:focus { outline: none; }
  .markdown-preview { flex: 1; padding: var(--space-4); overflow-y: auto; background: var(--color-bg); }
  .markdown-preview h1 { font-size: var(--text-2xl); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; padding-bottom: var(--space-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .markdown-preview h2 { font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: 600; margin: var(--space-6) 0 var(--space-3) 0; padding-bottom: var(--space-1); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .markdown-preview h3 { font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 600; margin: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-2) 0; }
  .markdown-preview h4, .markdown-preview h5, .markdown-preview h6 { font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 600; margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-2) 0; }
  .markdown-preview p { margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; line-height: 1.7; }
  .markdown-preview a { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; }
  .markdown-preview a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .markdown-preview code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.9em; background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
  .markdown-preview pre { background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow-x: auto; margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; }
  .markdown-preview pre code { background: none; padding: 0; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
  .markdown-preview blockquote { border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4); background: var(--color-bg-alt); color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .markdown-preview blockquote p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .markdown-preview ul, .markdown-preview ol { margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; padding-left: var(--space-6); }
  .markdown-preview li { margin-bottom: var(--space-1); line-height: 1.6; }
  .markdown-preview hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin: var(--space-6) 0; }
  .markdown-preview img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--radius-md); }
  .markdown-preview table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0; }
  .markdown-preview th, .markdown-preview td { border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); text-align: left; }
  .markdown-preview th { background: var(--color-bg-alt); font-weight: 600; }
  .markdown-preview .task-list-item { list-style: none; margin-left: calc(-1 * var(--space-6)); }
  .markdown-preview .task-list-item input { margin-right: var(--space-2); }
  .markdown-stats { display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-muted); }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<div class="tool-container">
  <!-- Action Buttons -->
  <div class="tool-actions" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
    <button type="button" id="sample-md" class="btn btn-secondary">Load Sample</button>
    <button type="button" id="copy-html" class="btn btn-secondary">Copy HTML</button>
    <button type="button" id="clear-md" class="btn btn-ghost">Clear</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Editor and Preview -->
  <div class="markdown-container">
    <div class="markdown-panel">
      <div class="markdown-panel-header">
        <span class="markdown-panel-title">Markdown</span>
      </div>
      <textarea id="markdown-input" class="markdown-editor" placeholder="Write your Markdown here..." spellcheck="false"># Hello, Markdown!

Start typing to see the **live preview** on the right.

## Features Supported

- **Bold** and *italic* text
- [Links](https://onedevkit.com)
- `Inline code` and code blocks
- Lists (ordered and unordered)
- Blockquotes
- Tables
- And more!</textarea>
      <div class="markdown-stats">
        <span id="char-count">0 characters</span>
        <span id="word-count">0 words</span>
        <span id="line-count">0 lines</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="markdown-panel">
      <div class="markdown-panel-header">
        <span class="markdown-panel-title">Preview</span>
      </div>
      <div id="markdown-preview" class="markdown-preview"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- How to Use Section -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>How to Use</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">1</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Write Markdown</h3><p>Type or paste your Markdown content in the left editor panel.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">2</div><div class="step-content"><h3>See Live Preview</h3><p>Watch your formatted content render in real-time on the right panel.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">3</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Copy HTML</h3><p>Click "Copy HTML" to get the rendered HTML code for use in your projects.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Markdown Cheat Sheet -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Markdown Cheat Sheet</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-4);">
    <div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Text Formatting</h3>
      <pre style="font-size: var(--text-sm); background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--space-3); border-radius: var(--radius-md);">**bold**
*italic*
~~strikethrough~~
`inline code`</pre>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Headers</h3>
      <pre style="font-size: var(--text-sm); background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--space-3); border-radius: var(--radius-md);"># H1
## H2
### H3</pre>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Links & Images</h3>
      <pre style="font-size: var(--text-sm); background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--space-3); border-radius: var(--radius-md);">[link text](url)
![alt text](image.jpg)</pre>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Lists</h3>
      <pre style="font-size: var(--text-sm); background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: var(--space-3); border-radius: var(--radius-md);">- Unordered item
1. Ordered item
- [ ] Task item</pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">What Markdown features are supported?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>This editor supports GitHub Flavored Markdown (GFM) including: headers, bold, italic, strikethrough, links, images, code blocks, blockquotes, lists, tables, task lists, and horizontal rules.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Can I export the HTML?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes! Click the "Copy HTML" button to copy the rendered HTML to your clipboard. You can then paste it into your website or application.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Is syntax highlighting supported?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Code blocks are rendered with basic formatting. Specify a language after the opening backticks (e.g., ```javascript) for proper display.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Is my content saved?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Content is not automatically saved. Copy your Markdown or HTML before leaving the page if you want to keep it.</p></div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Related Tools -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Related Tools</h2>
  <div class="related-tools">
    {% for tool in tools %}
    {% if tool.id != toolId %}
    <a href="/tools/{{ tool.id }}/" class="related-tool-link">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" width="16" height="16">{{ tool.icon | safe }}</svg>
      {{ tool.name }}
    </a>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
